Company Overview of XL Insurance (Bermuda) Ltd



Snapshot People




Company Overview
XL Insurance (Bermuda) Ltd offers property, casualty, professional, and specialty insurance and reinsurance products and services to industrial and commercial enterprises. It offers corporate risk, professional lines, and alternative risk transfer products. The company also provides life reinsurance services. XL Insurance (Bermuda) Ltd was formerly known as X.L. Insurance Company Ltd. and changed its name to XL Insurance (Bermuda) Ltd in January 1987. The company was founded in 1986 and is based in Hamilton, Bermuda with a branch office in San Francisco, California. XL Insurance (Bermuda) Ltd operates as a subsidiary of Exel Holdings Limited.


XL HouseOne Bermudiana RoadHamilton,  HM 11BermudaFounded in 1986



Phone: 441-292-8515

Fax: 441-292-9536








