 Career History



Vice President-New Product Development

                                    Current                


XL Insurance (Bermuda) Ltd.


                  XL Insurance (Bermuda) Ltd. provides liability insurance coverage services. The firm offers insurance and reinsurance coverages, and financial products & services to industrial, commercial, and professional service firms, insurance companies, and other enterprises worldwide. The company has operating divisions in Australia, the Czech Republic, France, Hungary, and Ireland. The company was established in 1986 and is headquartered in Hamilton, Bermuda.                





