Places to Stay
 







Places to Stay


 















Say Hello to Your Island Hideaway
From historic oceanfront resorts to intimate cottage colonies tucked into the hillsides, Bermuda offers many idyllic choices for where to stay. Private beaches, rolling golf courses, fine dining and attention-to-detail service are just some of the perks you'll find. The island's hotels, resorts, bed-and-breakfasts and historic inns are all dedicated to making your time here positively heavenly. After a few days, you'll understand why Mark Twain famously said, "You can go to heaven if you want. I'd rather stay in Bermuda."
 




 









Hotels & Resorts
 From golf courses and spas to great onsite dining, discover all the amenities you desire.
Explore Hotels & Resorts


Inns, Bed & Breakfasts & Guest Houses
 For an intimate island hideaway, retreat to a cosy B&B, quaint inn or historic guest house.
Explore Inns, Bed & Breakfasts & Guest Houses


Suites, Apartments & Cottages
 Spread out and ease into island life in a luxury suite, city apartment or waterfront cottage.
Explore Suites, Apartments & Cottages


Private Clubs
 The most discerning travellers gravitate toward Bermuda's exclusive oceanfront clubs.
Explore Private Clubs




 







